        <abstract>
            <p>Asks him to thank A. S. Taylor for note.</p> 
<p>Describes experiments on <hi rend="italic">Drosera</hi>.</p>  
<p>Discusses reviews of the <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi>. By far the best is by Asa Gray.</p>  
<p>Discusses plans for new edition of <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi>.</p> 
        </abstract>
